column5: Absolutly free: Are you looking for the trip of a lifetime, Québec has everything for you. Just enter the Québec Ultimate Destination Contest, the only giveaway where you could win your dream fishing or hunting trip to one of the Québec Outfitters! Enter the contest at: www.quebecultimatedestination.com Contest runs February 1st, to June 30th 2017 Watch the video for more info.https://youtu.be/UikL91ejlo4
Exactly and it's free, so nothing to loose. I can't participate because I live in the province of Quebec so if you win I'll be glad to join you
I revisited this offer and was surprised to learn one can enter both the fishing and hunting contest....yep, and I entered the hunting contest too.
Very neat looking trips. I look forward to winning!!
